title: Stars who were helped, hurt by free agency
itunes:title: Stars who were helped, hurt by free agency
description:
A room filled with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- react to the latest news around the NFL, recap the NFL Veteran's Combine and discuss which star players gained or lost in free agency.
